# Build context hygiene for all policy backends — keep image builds
# deterministic and prevent host-side scratch dirs from bleeding into
# the image. Runtime data lives on the compose-mounted ./workspace
# (host: docker/workspace/) shared across policy containers.
#
# Build context is cyclo_brain/policy/ (parent of lerobot/, groot/, ...)
# so paths are written relative to that.

# Per-policy scratch
*/workspace/
*/.git/
*/.venv/
*/.cache/
*/*.log

# Python build artifacts
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.egg-info/

# Submodule build artifacts (huggingface/lerobot, NVIDIA/Isaac-GR00T, ...)
**/build/
**/dist/

# Don't bake doc-only files into images
**/INTEGRATION_REPORT.md
